<!DOCTYPE html> 
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Verdi Beach - Ресторант на плажа</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="~/assets/img/favicon.ico" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/assets/css/app.css" />
    <script src="~/assets/js/app.js" defer></script>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="wrapper">
      <main class="contact-main">
      <div class="contact-container">
        <section class="contact-hero">
          <h1 class="contact-title">Свържете се с нас</h1>
          <p class="contact-subtitle">Винаги сме на разположение за вашите въпроси, резервации и предложения!</p>
        </section>
        <section class="contact-info-section">
          <div class="contact-info-grid">
            <div class="contact-details">
              <h2>Информация</h2>
              <ul>
                <li><strong>Адрес:</strong> к.к. Св. Константин и Елена, първа линия <br><span class="contact-address-note">(до хотел Азалия бара)</span></li>
                <li><strong>Телефон:</strong> <a href="tel:+359888123456">+359 888 123 456</a></li>
                <li><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:someone@example.com">someone@example.com</a></li>
                <li><strong>Работно време:</strong> 9:00 – 18:00</li>
              </ul>
              <div class="contact-socials">
                <a href="https://www.instagram.com/verdi_beach/" title="Instagram" class="social-icon"><i class="fa-brands fa-instagram"></i></a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
        <section class="contact-map-section">
          <h2>Къде да ни намерите?</h2>
          <div class="contact-map-wrapper">
            <iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d22104.237576726642!2d27.987960119448392!3d43.23342335197477!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x40a4572c927b1849%3A0xcfee7fb277273145!2sVerdi%20Beach!5e1!3m2!1sen!2sbg!4v1753169979626!5m2!1sen!2sbg" width="100%" height="350" style="border:0; border-radius:16px; box-shadow:0 8px 32px rgba(44,62,80,0.15);" allowfullscreen="" loading="lazy" referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"></iframe>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>
      </main>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
